snippet.title: Life Is Strange: Double Exposure - Gameplay Overview Trailer | gamescom 2024
snippet.description: Max Caulfield is back. Learn about how her new timeline-warping powers and solve her friend's mysterious murder in Life Is Strange: Double Exposure, coming to Xbox Series X/S, PlayStation 5, Nintendo Switch, and PC on October 29.
